      <h2>What is bridge fit?</h2>
      <p>We designed our bridge fit option, a style with nose pads added at the bridge of our glasses, for customers who found that they needed or wanted a more secure fit. If you find that sunglasses without nose pads typically slide off your nose or rest on your cheeks, we recommend you try a bridge fit style. The nose pads do not alter the appearance of our sunglasses when worn, but they’ll provide a comfortable, secure, and snug fit on all faces. <a href="http://westwardleaning.com/products/asian-bridge-fit-wayfarer">We offer bridge fit in select styles.</a></p>
      
      <h2>What gift card amounts are available?</h2>
      <p>We offer gift cards for $50, $100, $150, and $200. <a href="http://westwardleaning.com/products/gift-card">You can find them here.</a></p>
      {{ 'gift-card-case.jpg' | asset_url | img_tag: 'Gift Card Case', 'gift-card-case' }}
      
