      <h2>Can you help me pick a pair?</h2>
      <p>We love that our sunglasses are universally flattering -— we designed them to look great on everyone, regardless of age, gender, or location. Therefore choosing between pairs depends fully on your personal style.</p>
      <p>If you would like personal advice in selecting a pair, please do not hesitate to email us on <a href='mailto:help@westwardleaning.com'>help@westwardleaning.com</a> and we’d be happy to help. We also offer a few suggestions in our <a href='/pages/westward-leaning-recommends'>gift guide</a> and our <a href='/pages/lookbook'>street style</a>.</p>
      
