      <div id="shipping-and-exchanges">
      <h2>Where can I buy Westward Leaning sunglasses in my city?</h2>
      <p>The most complete selection of our available styles will always be found on our website. We are privileged to have partnered with incredible retailers around the world that each carry a selection of our collection. Please visit our <a href='/pages/stores'>stores page</a> for a complete list of our retail partners.</p>
      
      <h2>Do I need to create an account in order to place my order?</h2>
      <p>No. At this time we do not offer the ability to create a customer account and so orders are placed as a guest.</p>
      
      <h2>What payment options do you accept?</h2>
      <p>We accept all major credit cards (Visa, Mastercard, and Amex), as well as PayPal.</p>
      
      <h2>Is my payment secure?</h2>
      <p>We take security very seriously and guarantee a secure payment process.</p>
      
      <h2>Can I use my gift card more than once? Can I use more than one gift card at a time?</h2>
      <p>Gift cards are valid for one purchase only, and we only accept one gift card per purchase.</p>
      
      <h2>How long does it take to process an order?</h2>
      <p>Orders placed by 2pm PST, Monday through Friday, will ship that same day. Orders received after 2pm PST, or over the weekend, will be shipped the next business day.</p>
      <p>You will receive a confirmation email after placing your order and a second email upon shipment.</p>
      
      <h2>How can I check the status of my order?</h2>
      <p>You will receive an email after your order has been processed with tracking information for your package.</p>
      
      <h2>Where do you ship?</h2>
      <p>Westward Leaning is pleased to offer shipping worldwide. Please note that we do not ship to PO boxes.</p>
      
      <h2>What types of shipping do you offer? What does shipping cost?</h2>
      <p>We regularly offer discounted shipping options. For domestic (within the United States) orders, we always offer complimentary FedEx ground shipping. Depending on how far away you are from San Francisco, ground shipping will take anywhere between one and five business days. US-based customers may also request overnight shipping at checkout.</p>
      <p>For international orders, shipping costs a $25 flat rate. We ship through FedEx, and orders typically arrive within 3 business days.</p>
      {{ 'shipping-august.jpg' | asset_url | img_tag }}
      
      <h2>Can I expedite my order?</h2>
      <p>Yes, simply select expedited shipping in checkout.</p>
      
      <h2>Why/how much do I have to pay for duties and import taxes on orders shipped outside the US?</h2>
      <p>Many countries levy duties and import taxes on products shipped from other countries. Unfortunately, these customs charges are entirely outside our control and are not calculated at checkout. If such charges apply, FedEx will typically contact you after delivery of your sunglasses.</p>
      <p>For more information on what to expect in terms of import taxes in your country, <a href="http://export.gov/logistics/eg_main_018142.asp">please check here</a>.</p>
      
      <h2>Does Westward Leaning insure packages? Do I have to sign for delivery?</h2>
      <p>Westward Leaning does not insure packages, and no signature is required for delivery.</p>
      
      <h2>Can I change or cancel my order?</h2>
      <p>You can change or cancel your order until 1pm on the day that your package will be shipped.</p>
      
      <h2>How long do I have to make a return?</h2>
      <p>We accept returns within 30 days of your receipt of the sunglasses. Once we’ve received your return, we will credit you a full refund. Return shipping is free for domestic orders.</p>
      
      <h2>Can I exchange my sunglasses for a different pair?</h2>
      <p>Yes. If exchanging a pair for a different pair, we will ship you a new pair as soon as we receive the original pair in our office. To arrange an exchange, please contact help@westwardleaning.com.</p>
      
      <h2>What if I lose or break my sunglasses?</h2>
      <p>We guarantee the craftsmanship of our sunglasses. However, we cannot offer a replacement or exchange for any products that are lost or damaged due to misuse, negligence, or normal wear-and-tear.</p>
      
      <h2>I’ve broken my sunglasses. Can you send me loose screws, lenses, or swatches with which to repair them?</h2>
      <p>We do not ship loose parts, just whole sunglasses. Contact us on <a href='help@westwardleaning.com'>help@westwardleaning.com</a> to learn more.</p>

